               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmmǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 1va-108vb)&#xD; I-1)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka “I worship Thy Godhead…” (fols. 1va-2vb)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introduction (fols. 3ra-8rb)&#xD; - On John the Evangelist as the author of the
                     book; on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols. 3ra-5rb)&#xD; - Story
                     of the family of Adam (fols. 5rb-8rb)&#xD; I-3) Taʾāmmǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of
                     Jesus”: 42 miracles (fols. 8rb-108vb)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
